arCallbacks.szOnCallbackCompleteScript:
function Start(idActorPlayer, sWorldName)

	idVasekRun = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Frac_Depths_Sewer_Vasek")[1]
	idVasekRunLoc = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Frac_Depths_Sewer_VasekRunLoc")[1]
	followerOctavia = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("QST_Frac_DepthsOfDespair_Octavia_Follower")
	Hydra.Wait(0.3)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idVasekRun, idVasekRunLoc, "NPC_Sprint", false)
	Hydra.QActorDelete(idVasekRun)
	Hydra.Wait(0.5)
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(convStartCallout, followerOctavia)
	
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	followerOctavia = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("QST_Frac_DepthsOfDespair_Octavia_Follower")
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerOctavia) then
		Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(convCallout1, followerOctavia)
	end

end

	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerOctavia) then
		Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(convCallout2, followerOctavia)
	end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	followerOctavia = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("QST_Frac_DepthsOfDespair_Octavia_Follower")
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerOctavia) then
		Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(convCallout3, followerOctavia)
	end

end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	idStaticOctavia = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Frac_MaladyOfTheSoul_Octavia")[1]
	idVasek = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorDetector, "Vasek")[1]
	idChaliceGhostly = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorDetector, "ChaliceGhostly")[1]
	idBossSpawner = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorDetector, "Spawner")[1]
	idOctaviaMoveToLoc = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorDetector, "OctaviaMoveToLoc")[1]
	idOctaviaChaliceLoc = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorDetector, "OctaviaChaliceLoc")[1]
	idOctaviaLeaveLoc = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorDetector, "OctaviaLeaveLoc")[1]
	idFrozenVasek = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorDetector, "FrozenVasek")[1]
	
	followerOctavia = idActor
	Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(followerOctavia)
	Hydra.ActorDisableAI(followerOctavia)
	Hydra.QActorSheath(followerOctavia)
	Hydra.ActorSetAIState(followerOctavia, "idle")
	Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(convSeeVasek, followerOctavia)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(followerOctavia, idStaticOctavia, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(followerOctavia , idStaticOctavia)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(followerOctavia)
	Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(convSeeVasek)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(idStaticOctavia)
	Hydra.ActorDelete(followerOctavia)
	
	


end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)

	Hydra.ItemGiveQuestItemToPlayer(idActorPlayer, itemChalice, "DSQ_Frac_DepthsOfDespair_Sewer")
	Hydra.ActorEnable(idChaliceGhostly)
	
	Hydra.Wait(0.65)
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(convDistract, idStaticOctavia, idVasek)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idStaticOctavia, idOctaviaMoveToLoc, "NPC_Walk", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idStaticOctavia, idOctaviaMoveToLoc)
	
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)
	
	Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(convDistract)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idStaticOctavia, idOctaviaChaliceLoc, "NPC_Walk_Fast", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idStaticOctavia, idOctaviaChaliceLoc)
	Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(convDistract)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idStaticOctavia)
	
	Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(idStaticOctavia, "NPC_Idle_CutHand")
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(convRitual, idStaticOctavia, idVasek)
	
	Hydra.QActorWait(idStaticOctavia, 4)
	Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(idStaticOctavia)
	Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(idStaticOctavia, "NPC_Idle_Stand_Prayer_Sky")
	
	Hydra.QActorWait(idVasek, 3)
	Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(idVasek)
	Hydra.QActorFaceActor(idVasek, idStaticOctavia)
	Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(idVasek, "NPC_Scream")
	Hydra.QActorWait(idVasek, 10)
	Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(idVasek, "NPC_Idle_Stand_Scared_01")
	
end

function Start()
	
	Hydra.Wait(2)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idChaliceGhostly, fxHoly, true)
	Hydra.Wait(5)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroupActorToActor(idChaliceGhostly, idVasek, fxHolyRope, true, "HP_bladeCenter", "HP_chest")
	Hydra.Wait(8)
	Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(idStaticOctavia)
	Hydra.Wait(2)
	Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffectByEffectGroupSNO(idChaliceGhostly, fxHoly)
	Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffectByEffectGroupSNO(idChaliceGhostly, fxHolyRope)
	Hydra.Wait(9)
	Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(idFrozenVasek, 5)
	Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(idBossSpawner, 5)
	Hydra.ActorDisable(idVasek)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(idFrozenVasek)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idFrozenVasek, fxColdBurst)
	Hydra.Wait(1)
	Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(convRitual)
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(convFreezeReact, idStaticOctavia)
	
	Hydra.Wait(2)
	
	Hydra.ActorEnable(idBossSpawner)
	Hydra.Wait(0.2)
	Hydra.ActorGizmoOperate(idFrozenVasek)
	
end

function Start(idActorSpawned, idActorSpawner)

	Hydra.ActorDisableAI(idActorSpawned)
	Hydra.Wait(0.5)
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(convBossTaunt, idActorSpawned)
	Hydra.Wait(1.5)
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idActorSpawned)
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idStaticOctavia)
	
	
end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	
	Hydra.ActorDisableAI(idStaticOctavia)
	
	tPlayers = Hydra.PlayerActorsInLevelArea("QST_Frac_MaladyoftheSoul_Boss")
	
	Hydra.Wait(0.5)
	for i, Player in ipairs(tPlayers) do
		Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(convBossDies, Player)
	end
	
	Hydra.Wait(3)
	Hydra.ActorSetSheathPreference(idStaticOctavia, 1)
	Hydra.QActorSheath(idStaticOctavia)
	Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(idStaticOctavia, "NPC_NonCombat_HTH_Wounded")
	Hydra.QActorWait(idStaticOctavia, 2)
	Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(convBossDies)
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(convOctaviaLeaves, idStaticOctavia)
	Hydra.QActorWait(idStaticOctavia, 8)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idStaticOctavia, idOctaviaLeaveLoc, "NPC_Walk", false)
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idStaticOctavia, 0.5)

end
